data.description: Rare opportunity in the amazing community of Lake Arrowhead. Nestled in the Foothills of the North Georgia mountains this Private Gated Community with a 540 Acre lake offers a wonderful lifestyle. This project is a Homeowner or Builder/Investors dream! The existing home is MOVE-IN READY and sits on 0.98 acre lot. It was fully renovated in 2011. The Roof and HVAC systems are both 12 years old. This sale also includes a 2nd BUILDABLE lot on 0.73 acres right next door! TWO PROJECTS-IN-ONE: Renovate the existing home and build a new home next door (or use the lot as additional yard space!). New construction (and smaller) homes in the community are selling in the $600K's. Buyer can take advantage of the 5-star amenities that this community has to offer, including championship golf course, marina, clubhouse with restaurant, miles of hiking trails, 2 pools, tennis courts, pickle ball and so much more!
